```{r pancreas 32993498, include=FALSE}

PMID_32993498 <- RefManageR::ReadPubMed('32993498', database = 'PubMed')

PubMed_32993498 <- paste0(PubMedString, PMID_32993498$eprint)

doi_32993498 <- paste0(doiString, PMID_32993498$doi)

Sys.sleep(1)

```
